headline: The Nuclear Company Joins Forces With Nucor to Revive U.S. Nuclear Supply Chain
summary: The Nuclear Company has signed a strategic agreement with Nucor Corporation to rebuild the U.S. nuclear supply chain, aligning with federal initiatives to expand nuclear power and reduce reliance on foreign manufacturing.
